        <h3>SDS Requirements</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Solstice Disovery Service must be installed on a Windows machine with a static IP address running Windows 8 or 10, or a Windows Server running 2012 R2  or later, and a quad core processor with a minimum of 12GB RAM. A Windows 2016 Server may be used if desktop experience is enabled. </li>
        </ul>
